subject: Automobile Racing
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: Denny Hamlin is still in the running for the Nascar Nextel Cup championship, so it was not much of a surprise that he was leading the Raybestos Rookie of the Year standings with three races left.
